{"tid":1440542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日機場和你飛 所見所聞一二事","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:53:55.000Z","uid":251292,"like":439,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9ffef90ad9254f18142cfb7816a64440e662577f","tid":1440542,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:48:34.000Z","msg":"咁我今日去左機場係7樓好客地迎接各位就快離開香港既旅客啦 有幾件小事想share下<br />\n<br />\n 1. 我舉既牌其中一個係寫<br />\n&ldquo;Hong Kong Police fired expired tear gas.&rdquo;<br />\n居然有個鬼佬同我講<span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;This is not true&rdquo; </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟佢係警隊入面既人丫，定係點，不得而知了。<br />\n<br />\n2. 基本上有好多外國旅客都知大概係咩事，都有同好多係機場既手足講&rdquo; Good luck, we support you.&rdquo;<br />\n但咁岩比我見到有個類似猶太人(不能肯定來自邊到）<br />\n接左一個女仔既文宣係佢地面前然後撕爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後仲係到舉中指 我同佢講&rdquo;Behave yourself&rdquo;<br />\n佢繼續中指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多外國人都見到 梗係講&rdquo;so rude&rdquo;啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便我當然煮重佢米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 另外一個就係都有呀叔挑機<br />\n前一分鐘同佢個friend講緊廣東話<br />\n跟住自己走埋黎用英文同我講識唔識講英文<br />\n我梗係話識啦，等左呢個機會好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續用英文問我邊到黎，話香港警察唔係全部都係壞人，手指指住個腦叫我用腦諗野。<br />\n回左佢一句香港警察佢地係一team人，佢就頭也不回&rdquo;瀟灑&rdquo;走去國泰counter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔係真係覺得大家都係廢青呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實係機場既手足們係好有禮貌，解釋香港咩事，收到好多既鼓勵，機場和你飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3a3aba91d8dc4574c0c0229618e64e7c4a4e3f","tid":1440542,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0278c59025e70f8198040b8fbed03e883ceba322","tid":1440542,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee1491a8b503eb8571a38b0207c5aa08a716f3a","tid":1440542,"uid":251292,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score":136,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"今日見到真係笑左出黎<br />\n另外仲聽到有個妹妹問：點解佢地可以堅持左成日咁耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvawLEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvawLEz.jpg&h=38f5182e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a6df9a1e93be65187f629a9a0af7d8fe8f56900","tid":1440542,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9f4812a78889dd73a71bf834b1b484aa83eb1f","tid":1440542,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e924bf709ea648eff8dc73d0d3485ffd865aa50","tid":1440542,"uid":302917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"我地要繼續加油，持久戰嚟"},{"pid":"4894b81056d7462b4a9105bbccc94d6822e200de","tid":1440542,"uid":264362,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:59:33.000Z","msg":"預到挑機既人可以唔洗理佢，始終冇可能每個人都支持"},{"pid":"b0fe22bd07daf92bf557d9f417dc1314beb84e1b","tid":1440542,"uid":283665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fee1491a8b503eb8571a38b0207c5aa08a716f3a","tid":1440542,"uid":251292,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score":136,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"今日見到真係笑左出黎<br />\n另外仲聽到有個妹妹問：點解佢地可以堅持左成日咁耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvawLEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvawLEz.jpg&h=38f5182e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dd6a4a43b5c4c006f76ef747f53c1ed32839a8","tid":1440542,"uid":251292,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:03:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到有個美國妹妹寫左大字報支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73de99485f2b1e9fe5e7018a18245ee1815a2d86","tid":1440542,"uid":304321,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"和你飛手足們加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09b6cefa5acb6c241755eabf17809bf9e47052b","tid":1440542,"uid":228955,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"有啲鬼佬比支那洗腦 例如去大陸做生意帶佢去叫雞"},{"pid":"502691640470f272c40d6b4c787a92d6aed49c4c","tid":1440542,"uid":251292,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a09b6cefa5acb6c241755eabf17809bf9e47052b","tid":1440542,"uid":228955,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"有啲鬼佬比支那洗腦 例如去大陸做生意帶佢去叫雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"又或者同支那狗做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614201f47d25e56c196fababe94fd00e1676945d","tid":1440542,"uid":2142,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"親眼所見<br />